# Session/working state, not product. This is DEVELOPMENT's current state —
# production has no use for dev session notes, and it churns every session.
# ⚠️ Untracked = no git history and no GitHub backup. If this box dies, it dies.
# Durable cross-environment knowledge (how to deploy, the two-env split, the
# test-suite guard, settled decisions) belongs in decisions.md / INSTALL.md /
# PRD.md — which stay tracked — NOT here.
docs/current-state.md
